    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "A layer renderer type creates a bridge between a SwiftUI scene",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "and the Metal code you use to draw fully immersive experiences.",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "When you present an immersive space with ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.compositorservices/documentation/CompositorServices/CompositorLayer",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " content,",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "the system creates a ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.compositorservices/documentation/CompositorServices/LayerRenderer",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " type and makes it available to the content’s closure.",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "Use the information in the layer to set up your app’s rendering loop,",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "and to start drawing frames of content.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Each layer has information that tells the system how to configure the Metal textures",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "and data types your app needs.",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "Compositor Services provides a default configuration for layers, but you can",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "customize the configuration of your layer as needed.",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "Specify your custom configuration details using the",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.compositorservices/documentation/CompositorServices/CompositorLayerConfiguration",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " protocol and pass a type with those details to",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "the initializer for your immersive space’s content .",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "Use the layer’s capability information to validate any configuration choices you make.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "For information about how to create and configure a layer and use it to run your rendering loop,",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "see ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.compositorservices/documentation/CompositorServices/drawing-fully-immersive-content-using-metal",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
